pageProduct.name: Ostelin Bone Strength + Iron 60 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
Information

Why Bone Strength matters

Reaching peak bone mass

Strong bones are essential for quality of life, as bones provide the structure for our bodies*. Peak bone mass is reached in our 20s**, but no matter your age, it will make a difference to make decisions that support long-term bone strength. Consuming enough vitamin D and calcium is one way to achieve this.

*Better Health Channel. Bones. 2012

**Mitchell PJ et al. Life-course approach to nutrition. Osteoporos Int. 2015, 26(12), 2723 2742

Bone Strength Iron

Iron supports energy production. Ostelin Bone Strength Iron provides Vitamin D, a key nutrient to maintain bone strength, plus iron to support energy production and maintain iron levels in the body. It contains a bioavailable form of iron plus Vitamin C to support the absorption of iron in the body.

Dosage for Adults: Take 2 tablets daily with a meal or as directed by your healthcare professional.

Ostelin Bone Strength Iron Product Benefits

Contains iron to support energy production and maintain iron levels in the body.

Contains vitamin D3, an important nutrient as it maintains bone strength.

Contains vitamin C, which supports the absorption of iron in the body.

No added gluten, lactose, dairy products, artificial flavours or sweeteners.

General Information

Maintain bone strength.
Maintains iron levels in the body.
Supports energy production.

• Ostelin Bone Strength + Iron provides vitamin D, a key nutrient to maintain bone strength plus iron to support energy production and maintain iron levels in the body.
• It contains a bioavailable form of iron plus vitamin C to support the absorption of iron in the body.
• Vitamin D3 is a key nutrient as it helps maintain bone strength.

Size: 60 Tablets

KEY FEATURES

• Contains vitamin D3: To maintain bone strength
• Contains iron: To support energy production and maintain iron levels in the body
• Contains vitamin C: To support the absorption of iron into the body
• Dosage: Take 2 tablets daily with a meal or as directed by your healthcare professional
• This medicine may not be right for you. Read the warnings before purchase, in warnings section below. Follow the directions for use.

Warnings

Contains soya and sulfur dioxide.

Ingredients

Iron (from Iron II glycinate) 12mg
Colecalciferol (Vitamin D3 500IU) 12.5micrograms
Calcium ascorbate dihydrate (Vitamin C 50mg) 60.52mg
Calcium Pantothenate (Vitamin B5) 2mg
Pyridoxine Hydrochloride (Vitamin B6) 2.5mg
Folic Acid 200 micrograms

Contains: NO ADDED: Gluten, lactose, artificial flavours, artificial sweeteners, or dairy products.

Contains Soya and sulfur dioxide.

Halal certified.

Directions

For adults: take 2 tablets daily with a meal or as directed by your healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C.
Protect from moisture.
